{
  "stem": "95.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But-- but you do that, and I'll give you an example of why we did not know that we were going to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The first day on the train-- my mother was really a saint and, a wonderful woman, and very wise.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was not educated, but she was a very wise person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She asked me to write a letter to my brother, Jaques, the first day on the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And even though-- the train stopped once in awhile because either there were convoys of soldiers going someplace, and they had to stop, and they would go back, and we would hear some French speaking language the first day.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother would say, write that letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she'd tell me what to write.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in the letter-- I mean, I'm kind of paraphrasing here because I don't want to go through the whole letter-- I said, Dear Jaques, we are 100 people in each compartment.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It is so terrible, what's happening in them, I don't want to describe it, and I hope that you will never see it for the rest of your life.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I mention all the names of the family who was on the train with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I said in the letter, I said, we have hope, and we have courage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we hope to join some of the sisters who were deported before us, in the resettlement camp in Metz, which is northeast of France.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we hope to come back and be a united family all over again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's trivia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't think she told me to write that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's only trivia like, excuse my handwriting, but the train is in motion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I said, take care of yourself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Take care of your family.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
